{"tid":122614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一句「顧客永遠是對的」害死左香港","createTime":"2017-02-16T07:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T07:35:31.000Z","uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b258e0ffaebd7530fa0fa6571d7a422abbeb6ab","tid":122614,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"仲有「今時今日咁既服務態度係唔得架」呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到啲客愈來愈離譜 愈來愈西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲例子真係講極都唔完：食完番來話唔好食咪投訴退錢又有/監生話你標錯價要投訴退錢又有 /豬展入面有舊豬軟骨又可以話你呃錢<br />\n<br />\n香港人可唔可以唔好咁西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然我唔否認有服務員都係西 但係講西一定唔夠啲客西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d17090555d61433f3430ccf4a362e2aa02ea491","tid":122614,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"真你好認同 有陣時真係心諗 屌你老味真係比幾蚊當自己皇帝咩<br />\n利申 唔係做服務性行業 但真係睇唔過眼d 人少少野就屌人 投訴人"},{"pid":"20841a3084d781822a6c1fe0512c5e9dbfe58102","tid":122614,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"呢句野好似都由外國引入，<br />\n不過亦都out左好耐。<br />\n<br />\n所以而家亦都有極多西面sales<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇西面sales係因為西面客<br />\n同時西面客亦都係因為西面sales"},{"pid":"4c7b613fe7de0bc63aa8f00ead2bb5a5f9dd8d83","tid":122614,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢句野好似都由外國引入，<br />\n不過亦都out左好耐。<br />\n<br />\n所以而家亦都有極多西面sales<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇西面sales係因為西面客<br />\n同時西面客亦都係因為西面sales</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入晒心啦 邊有out過<br />\n最後果句係一定既<br />\n因為冤冤相報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796055d96b9d57761cbdf607a2ac1662750dda36","tid":122614,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":